#A long-bladed [[knife]] that is longer than a [[dagger]] and is designed to stab, cut and [[slash]] a victim.  It was sheathed in a [[scabbard]].  It was originally a [[melee|mel&eacute;e]] weapon that was used in serious combat, but now is mostly used in sports and for ceremonies, and is viewed as one of the most noble weapons.

